# 1. PROBLEM SUMMARY\
\
The cross-chapter exhaustion system is working. Insights are no longer re-explained after their owning chapter.\
\
However, **within** the owning chapter:\
- EXPLAIN is unlimited 
\f9 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  same insight restated 6-10 times\
- DEMONSTRATE is unlimited 
\f9 \uc0\u8594 
\f0  bloated example lists (11 identity statements)\
\
This produces books that are architecturally correct but still repetitive.\
\
