## 2.2 Governor 2: Demonstration Saturation Cap\
\
### Rule\
\

\f12 Per insight, per chapter:\
  DEMONSTRATE beats allowed: max_demonstrate (default: 3)\
  Additional DEMONSTRATE beats: WARN (default) or FAIL (strict)
\f0 \
\
### Rationale\
\
Demonstration is valuable, but more than 3 examples creates bloat. The listener understood after the second example.\
\
### Implementation\
\

